{
  "id": "MAT.17",
  "bibleId": "de4e12af7f28f599-01",
  "number": "17",
  "bookId": "MAT",
  "reference": "Matthew 17",
  "copyright": "PUBLIC DOMAIN except in the United Kingdom, where a Crown Copyright applies to printing the KJV. See http://www.cambridge.org/about-us/who-we-are/queens-printers-patent",
  "verseCount": 27,
  "content": [
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And after six days Jesus taketh Peter, James, and John his brother, and bringeth them up into an high mountain apart, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And was transfigured before them: and his face did shine as the sun, and his raiment was white as the light. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And, behold, there appeared unto them Moses and Elias talking with him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then answered Peter, and said unto Jesus, Lord, it is good for us to be here: if thou wilt, let us make here three tabernacles; one for thee, and one for Moses, and one for Elias. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "While he yet spake, behold, a bright cloud overshadowed them: and behold a voice out of the cloud, which said, This is my beloved Son, in whom I am well pleased; hear ye him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And when the disciples heard ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "it",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", they fell on their face, and were sore afraid. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And Jesus came and touched them, and said, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Arise, and be not afraid.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.7",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.7"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And when they had lifted up their eyes, they saw no man, save Jesus only. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And as they came down from the mountain, Jesus charged them, saying, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Tell the vision to no man, until the Son of man be risen again from the dead.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.9",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.9"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And his disciples asked him, saying, Why then say the scribes that Elias must first come? ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "11",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:11"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "11",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And Jesus answered and said unto them, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Elias truly shall first come, and restore all things.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.11",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.11"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "12",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:12"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "12",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "But I say unto you, That Elias is come already, and they knew him not, but have done unto him whatsoever they listed. Likewise shall also the Son of man suffer of them.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.12",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.12"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "13",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:13"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "13",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then the disciples understood that he spake unto them of John the Baptist.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.13"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "14",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:14"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "14",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ And when they were come to the multitude, there came to him a ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "certain",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.14",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.14"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " man, kneeling down to him, and saying, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "15",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:15"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "15",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Lord, have mercy on my son: for he is lunatick, and sore vexed: for ofttimes he falleth into the fire, and oft into the water. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "16",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:16"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "16",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And I brought him to thy disciples, and they could not cure him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "17",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:17"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "17",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then Jesus answered and said, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "O faithless and perverse generation, how long shall I be with you? how long shall I suffer you? bring him hither to me.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.17",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.17"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "18",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:18"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "18",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And Jesus rebuked the devil; and he departed out of him: and the child was cured from that very hour. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.18"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "19",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:19"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "19",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then came the disciples to Jesus apart, and said, Why could not we cast him out? ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.19",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.19"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "20",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:20"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "20",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And Jesus said unto them, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.20"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Because of your unbelief: for verily I say unto you, If ye have faith as a grain of mustard seed, ye shall say unto this mountain, Remove hence to yonder place; and it shall remove; and nothing shall be impossible unto you.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.20"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.20"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "21",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:21"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "21",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Howbeit this kind goeth not out but by prayer and fasting.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.21",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.21"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "22",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:22"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "22",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ And while they abode in Galilee, Jesus said unto them, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.22",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.22"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "The Son of man shall be betrayed into the hands of men:",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.22",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.22"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.22",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.22"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "23",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:23"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "23",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "And they shall kill him, and the third day he shall be raised again.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.23",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.23"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " And they were exceeding sorry.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.23",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.23"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "24",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:24"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "24",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ And when they were come to Capernaum, they that received tribute ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.24",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.24"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "money",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.24",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.24"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " came to Peter, and said, Doth not your master pay tribute? ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.24",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.24"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "25",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:25"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "25",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "He saith, Yes. And when he was come into the house, Jesus prevented him, saying, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.25",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.25"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "What thinkest thou, Simon? of whom do the kings of the earth take custom or tribute? of their own children, or of strangers?",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.25",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.25"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.25",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.25"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "26",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 17:26"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "26",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Peter saith unto him, Of strangers. Jesus saith unto him, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.17.26",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.17.26"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Then are the children free.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.17.26",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.17.26"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
